@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Me";
}

<section class="py-16 px-6" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
        <!-- Profile Image -->
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Your Profile Picture"
            class="rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg w-48 sm:w-56 md:w-64 lg:w-72">

        <!-- Introduction Text -->
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 md:text-4xl md:text-left">Hi, I'm Petrine</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 text-lg text-left">
            I'm a passionate developer from Bergen, with a love for clean code and creating digital solutions that are
            both functional and user-friendly.
        </p>

        <!-- Personal Interests -->
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 text-lg text-left">
            When I'm not coding, you'll find me involved in dog sports, climbing, exploring the outdoors, and spending
            quality time with my family. I'm also a volunteer with the Røde Kors, currently training to become certified
            in
            search and rescue operations.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Small Image Row -->
    <div class="container mx-auto mt-12">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <!-- Image 1 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x150" alt="Project 1"
                    class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-lg">
            </div>

            <!-- Image 2 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x150" alt="Project 2"
                    class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-lg">
            </div>

            <!-- Image 3 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x150" alt="Project 3"
                    class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-lg">
            </div>

            <!-- Image 4 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x150" alt="Project 4"
                    class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-lg">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-16 px-6" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-6">My Journey in IT</h2>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 text-left">
            My journey into IT started with a deep passion for <strong>JavaScript</strong>, a language that has truly
            captivated me due to its versatility and ability to bring ideas to life on the web. As a developer, I love
            exploring new technologies, and when building this site, I chose to use ASP.NET Razor Pages to try something
            new and expand my skill set.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 text-left">
            In my design work, I focus on creating modern layouts with plenty of whitespace, allowing content to breathe
            and making information easier to read and navigate. I enjoy crafting user interfaces that are clean,
            engaging, and functional, aiming to give users a seamless experience. My approach centers around simplicity
            and readability, with a belief that well-designed spaces help users focus on what’s important.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 text-left">
            While I'm drawn to front-end design, I'm equally interested in exploring the back-end side of development in
            my spare time. Working with databases, APIs, and server-side logic adds depth to my skill set, enabling me
            to create more complete and dynamic applications. The opportunity to work across both ends of development
            has given me a deeper understanding of how to build robust, scalable solutions.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 text-left">
            This blend of front-end creativity and back-end logic keeps me engaged and constantly learning. Whether I'm
            experimenting with a new front-end framework or digging into server-side code, I enjoy the challenges and
            rewards that come with each project. My goal is to continue growing as a versatile developer who can bring a
            well-rounded perspective to any team or project.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="container mx-auto mt-12" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-6">Stacked Skills</h2>
    <div class="container max-w-4xl mx-auto flex items-end space-x-4 md:space-x-6 lg:space-x-8">

        <!-- Fun Measurement Labels on the Left -->
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-around h-80 mr-8">
            <span class="text-gray-600 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base">Code Ninja</span>
            <span class="text-gray-600 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base">Knows some stuff</span>
            <span class="text-gray-600 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base">Can Google it</span>
            <span class="text-gray-600 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base">Kaffe-deprived</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Bars and Skill Names -->
        <div class="flex space-x-4 md:space-x-6 lg:space-x-8 items-end" style="height: 350px;">

            <!-- Bar 1: HTML -->
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <div class="outer-bar bg-gray-200 w-12 sm:w-14 md:w-16 lg:w-18 h-full flex items-end">
                    <div class="inner-bar bg-red-400 w-full" style="height: 95%;"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="skill-name mt-2 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base">JavaScript</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Bar 2: CSS -->
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <div class="outer-bar bg-gray-200 w-12 sm:w-14 md:w-16 lg:w-18 h-full flex items-end">
                    <div class="inner-bar bg-green-400 w-full" style="height: 90%;"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="skill-name mt-2 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base">CSS</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Bar 3: JavaScript -->
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <div class="outer-bar bg-gray-200 w-12 sm:w-14 md:w-16 lg:w-18 h-full flex items-end">
                    <div class="inner-bar bg-blue-400 w-full" style="height: 50%;"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="skill-name mt-2 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base">Angular</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Bar 4: React -->
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <div class="outer-bar bg-gray-200 w-12 sm:w-14 md:w-16 lg:w-18 h-full flex items-end">
                    <div class="inner-bar bg-yellow-400 w-full" style="height: 40%;"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="skill-name mt-2 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base">.Net</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

